#. <section class="sutta" id="sn42.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn42.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 42"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 42"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn42.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Gāmaṇivagga"
msgstr "1. Chiefs"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 8. Saṅkhadhamasutta → saṅkha (pts1)
msgctxt "sn42.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Saṅkhadhamasutta"
msgstr "8. A Horn Blower"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.318"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā nāḷandāyaṃ viharati pāvārikambavane."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Nālandā in Pāvārika’s mango grove."

msgctxt "sn42.8:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho asibandhakaputto gāmaṇi nigaṇṭhasāvako yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho asibandhakaputtaṃ "
"gāmaṇiṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Asibandhaka’s son the chief, who was a disciple of the Jains, went up "
"to the Buddha, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "sn42.8:1.3"
msgid "“kathaṃ nu kho, gāmaṇi, nigaṇṭho nāṭaputto sāvakānaṃ dhammaṃ desetī”ti?"
msgstr "“Chief, how does Nigaṇṭha Nātaputta teach his disciples?”"

msgctxt "sn42.8:1.4"
msgid "“Evaṃ kho, bhante, nigaṇṭho nāṭaputto sāvakānaṃ dhammaṃ deseti:"
msgstr "“Sir, this is how Nigaṇṭha Nātaputta teaches his disciples:"

msgctxt "sn42.8:1.5"
msgid ""
"‘yo koci pāṇaṃ atipāteti, sabbo so āpāyiko nerayiko, yo koci adinnaṃ "
"ādiyati, sabbo so āpāyiko nerayiko, yo koci kāmesu micchā carati, sabbo so "
"āpāyiko nerayiko, yo koci musā bhaṇati sabbo, so āpāyiko nerayiko."
msgstr ""
"‘Everyone who kills a living creature, steal, commits sexual misconduct, or "
"lies goes to a place of loss, to hell."

msgctxt "sn42.8:1.6"
msgid "Yaṃbahulaṃ yaṃbahulaṃ viharati, tena tena nīyatī’ti."
msgstr "You’re led on by what you usually live by.’"

msgctxt "sn42.8:1.7"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhante, nigaṇṭho nāṭaputto sāvakānaṃ dhammaṃ desetī”ti."
msgstr "This is how Nigaṇṭha Nātaputta teaches his disciples.”"

msgctxt "sn42.8:1.8"
msgid ""
"“‘Yaṃbahulaṃ yaṃbahulañca, gāmaṇi, viharati, tena tena nīyati’, evaṃ sante "
"na koci āpāyiko nerayiko bhavissati, yathā nigaṇṭhassa nāṭaputtassa vacanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“‘You’re led on by what you usually live by’: if this were true, then, "
"according to what Nigaṇṭha Nātaputta says, no-one would go to a place of "
"loss, to hell."

# Here the Buddha invents time management.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:2.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, gāmaṇi, "
msgstr "What do you think, chief? "

msgctxt "sn42.8:2.2"
msgid ""
"yo so puriso pāṇātipātī rattiyā vā divasassa vā samayāsamayaṃ upādāya, "
"katamo bahutaro samayo, yaṃ vā so pāṇamatipāteti, yaṃ vā so pāṇaṃ "
"nātipātetī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Take a person who kills living creatures. If we compare periods of time "
"during the day and night, which is more frequent: the occasions when they’re "
"killing or when they’re not killing?”"

msgctxt "sn42.8:2.3"
msgid ""
"“Yo so, bhante, puriso pāṇātipātī rattiyā vā divasassa vā samayāsamayaṃ "
"upādāya, appataro so samayo yaṃ so pāṇamatipāteti, atha kho sveva bahutaro "
"samayo yaṃ so pāṇaṃ nātipātetī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“The occasions when they’re killing are less frequent, while the occasions "
"when they’re not killing are more frequent.”"

msgctxt "sn42.8:2.4"
msgid ""
"“‘Yaṃbahulaṃ yaṃbahulañca, gāmaṇi, viharati tena tena nīyatī’ti, evaṃ sante "
"na koci āpāyiko nerayiko bhavissati, yathā nigaṇṭhassa nāṭaputtassa vacanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“‘You’re led on by what you usually live by’: if this were true, then, "
"according to what Nigaṇṭha Nātaputta says, no-one would go to a place of "
"loss, to hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:3.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, gāmaṇi, "
msgstr "What do you think, chief? "

msgctxt "sn42.8:3.2"
msgid ""
"yo so puriso adinnādāyī rattiyā vā divasassa vā samayāsamayaṃ upādāya, "
"katamo bahutaro samayo, yaṃ vā so adinnaṃ ādiyati, yaṃ vā so adinnaṃ "
"nādiyatī”ti."
msgstr "Take a person who steals …"

msgctxt "sn42.8:3.3"
msgid ""
"“Yo so, bhante, puriso adinnādāyī rattiyā vā divasassa vā samayāsamayaṃ "
"upādāya appataro so samayo, yaṃ so adinnaṃ ādiyati, atha kho sveva bahutaro "
"samayo, yaṃ so adinnaṃ nādiyatī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:3.4"
msgid ""
"“‘Yaṃbahulaṃ yaṃbahulañca, gāmaṇi, viharati tena tena nīyatī’ti, evaṃ sante "
"na koci āpāyiko nerayiko bhavissati, yathā nigaṇṭhassa nāṭaputtassa vacanaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.319"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:4.1"
msgid ""
"Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, gāmaṇi, yo so puriso kāmesumicchācārī rattiyā vā divasassa "
"vā samayāsamayaṃ upādāya, katamo bahutaro samayo, yaṃ vā so kāmesu micchā "
"carati, yaṃ vā so kāmesu micchā na caratī”ti?"
msgstr "commits sexual misconduct …"

msgctxt "sn42.8:4.2"
msgid ""
"“Yo so, bhante, puriso kāmesumicchācārī rattiyā vā divasassa vā "
"samayāsamayaṃ upādāya, appataro so samayo yaṃ so kāmesu micchā carati, atha "
"kho sveva bahutaro samayo, yaṃ so kāmesu micchā na caratī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:4.3"
msgid ""
"“‘Yaṃbahulaṃ yaṃbahulañca, gāmaṇi, viharati tena tena nīyatī’ti, evaṃ sante "
"na koci āpāyiko nerayiko bhavissati, yathā nigaṇṭhassa nāṭaputtassa vacanaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:5.1"
msgid ""
"Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, gāmaṇi, yo so puriso musāvādī rattiyā vā divasassa vā "
"samayāsamayaṃ upādāya, katamo bahutaro samayo, yaṃ vā so musā bhaṇati, yaṃ "
"vā so musā na bhaṇatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"lies. If we compare periods of time during the day and night, which is more "
"frequent: the occasions when they’re lying or when they’re not lying?”"

msgctxt "sn42.8:5.2"
msgid ""
"“Yo so, bhante, puriso musāvādī rattiyā vā divasassa vā samayāsamayaṃ "
"upādāya, appataro so samayo, yaṃ so musā bhaṇati, atha kho sveva bahutaro "
"samayo, yaṃ so musā na bhaṇatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“The occasions when they’re lying are less frequent, while the occasions "
"when they’re not lying are more frequent.”"

msgctxt "sn42.8:5.3"
msgid ""
"“‘Yaṃbahulaṃ yaṃbahulañca, gāmaṇi, viharati tena tena nīyatī’ti, evaṃ sante "
"na koci āpāyiko nerayiko bhavissati, yathā nigaṇṭhassa nāṭaputtassa vacanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“‘You’re led on by what you usually live by’: if this were true, then, "
"according to what Nigaṇṭha Nātaputta says, no-one would go to a place of "
"loss, to hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.320"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: evaṃdiṭṭhi → evaṃdiṭṭhī (mr)
msgctxt "sn42.8:6.1"
msgid "Idha, gāmaṇi, ekacco satthā evaṃvādī hoti evaṃdiṭṭhi:"
msgstr "Take some teacher who has this doctrine and view:"

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.2"
msgid ""
"‘yo koci pāṇamatipāteti, sabbo so āpāyiko nerayiko, yo koci adinnaṃ ādiyati, "
"sabbo so āpāyiko nerayiko, yo koci kāmesu micchā carati, sabbo so āpāyiko "
"nerayiko, yo koci musā bhaṇati, sabbo so āpāyiko nerayiko’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Everyone who kills a living creature, steals, commits sexual misconduct, or "
"lies goes to a place of loss, to hell.’"

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.3"
msgid "Tasmiṃ kho pana, gāmaṇi, satthari sāvako abhippasanno hoti."
msgstr "And there’s a disciple who is devoted to that teacher."

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.4"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "They think:"

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.5"
msgid "‘mayhaṃ kho satthā evaṃvādī evaṃdiṭṭhi—"
msgstr "‘My teacher has this doctrine and view:"

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.6"
msgid "yo koci pāṇamatipāteti, sabbo so āpāyiko nerayikoti."
msgstr ""
"‘Everyone who kills a living creature, steals, commits sexual misconduct, or "
"lies goes to a place of loss, to hell.’"

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.7"
msgid ""
"Atthi kho pana mayā pāṇo atipātito, ahampamhi āpāyiko nerayikoti diṭṭhiṃ "
"paṭilabhati."
msgstr "But I’ve killed living creatures …"

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.8"
msgid ""
"Taṃ, gāmaṇi, vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ "
"appaṭinissajjitvā yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.9"
msgid "Mayhaṃ kho satthā evaṃvādī evaṃdiṭṭhi—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.10"
msgid "yo koci adinnaṃ ādiyati, sabbo so āpāyiko nerayikoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.11"
msgid ""
"Atthi kho pana mayā adinnaṃ ādinnaṃ ahampamhi āpāyiko nerayikoti diṭṭhiṃ "
"paṭilabhati."
msgstr "stolen …"

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.12"
msgid ""
"Taṃ, gāmaṇi, vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ "
"appaṭinissajjitvā yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.13"
msgid "Mayhaṃ kho satthā evaṃvādī evaṃdiṭṭhi—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.14"
msgid "yo koci kāmesu micchā carati, sabbo so āpāyiko nerayiko’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.15"
msgid "Atthi kho pana mayā kāmesu micchā ciṇṇaṃ."
msgstr "committed sexual misconduct …"

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.16"
msgid "‘Ahampamhi āpāyiko nerayiko’ti diṭṭhiṃ paṭilabhati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.17"
msgid ""
"Taṃ, gāmaṇi, vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ "
"appaṭinissajjitvā yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.18"
msgid "Mayhaṃ kho satthā evaṃvādī evaṃdiṭṭhi—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.19"
msgid "yo koci musā bhaṇati, sabbo so āpāyiko nerayikoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.20"
msgid "Atthi kho pana mayā musā bhaṇitaṃ."
msgstr "or lied."

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.21"
msgid "‘Ahampamhi āpāyiko nerayiko’ti diṭṭhiṃ paṭilabhati."
msgstr "They get the view: ‘I too am going to a place of loss, to hell.’"

msgctxt "sn42.8:6.22"
msgid ""
"Taṃ, gāmaṇi, vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ "
"appaṭinissajjitvā yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr ""
"Unless they give up that speech and thought, and let go of that view, they "
"will be cast down to hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:7.1"
msgid ""
"Idha pana, gāmaṇi, tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho "
"vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā "
"devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā."
msgstr ""
"But consider when a Realized One arises in the world, perfected, a fully "
"awakened Buddha, accomplished in knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the "
"world, supreme guide for those who wish to train, teacher of gods and "
"humans, awakened, blessed."

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.2"
msgid ""
"So anekapariyāyena pāṇātipātaṃ garahati vigarahati, ‘pāṇātipātā viramathā’ti "
"cāha."
msgstr ""
"In many ways he criticizes and denounces killing living creatures, saying: ‘"
"Stop killing living creatures!’"

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.3"
msgid "Adinnādānaṃ garahati vigarahati, ‘adinnādānā viramathā’ti cāha."
msgstr "He criticizes and denounces stealing …"

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.4"
msgid ""
"Kāmesumicchācāraṃ garahati, vigarahati ‘kāmesumicchācārā viramathā’ti cāha."
msgstr "sexual misconduct …"

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.5"
msgid "Musāvādaṃ garahati vigarahati ‘musāvādā viramathā’ti cāha."
msgstr "lying, saying: ‘Stop lying!’"

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.6"
msgid "Tasmiṃ kho pana, gāmaṇi, satthari sāvako abhippasanno hoti."
msgstr "And there’s a disciple who is devoted to that teacher."

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.7"
msgid "So iti paṭisañcikkhati:"
msgstr "Then they reflect:"

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.8"
msgid ""
"‘bhagavā kho anekapariyāyena pāṇātipātaṃ garahati vigarahati, pāṇātipātā "
"viramathāti cāha."
msgstr ""
"‘In many ways the Buddha criticizes and denounces killing living creatures, "
"saying: “Stop killing living creatures!”"

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.9"
msgid "Atthi kho pana mayā pāṇo atipātito yāvatako vā tāvatako vā."
msgstr "But I have killed living creatures to a certain extent."

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.10"
msgid ""
"Yo kho pana mayā pāṇo atipātito yāvatako vā tāvatako vā, taṃ na suṭṭhu, taṃ "
"na sādhu."
msgstr "That’s not right, it’s not good,"

#. VAR: Ahañceva → ahañce (?)
msgctxt "sn42.8:7.11"
msgid "Ahañceva kho pana tappaccayā vippaṭisārī assaṃ."
msgstr "and I feel remorseful because of it."

#. VAR: pāpaṃ kammaṃ → pāpakaṃ kammaṃ (bj) | pāpakammaṃ (s1-3, km, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn42.8:7.12"
msgid "Na metaṃ pāpaṃ kammaṃ akataṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr "But I can’t undo what I have done.’"

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.13"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya tañceva pāṇātipātaṃ pajahati."
msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up killing living creatures,"

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.14"
msgid "Āyatiñca pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr "and in future they don’t kill living creatures."

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.15"
msgid "Evametassa pāpassa kammassa pahānaṃ hoti."
msgstr "That’s how to give up this bad deed"

msgctxt "sn42.8:7.16"
msgid "Evametassa pāpassa kammassa samatikkamo hoti."
msgstr "and get past it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.321"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:8.1"
msgid ""
"‘Bhagavā kho anekapariyāyena adinnādānaṃ garahati vigarahati, adinnādānā "
"viramathāti cāha."
msgstr "‘In many ways the Buddha criticizes and denounces stealing …"

msgctxt "sn42.8:8.2"
msgid "Atthi kho pana mayā adinnaṃ ādinnaṃ yāvatakaṃ vā tāvatakaṃ vā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:8.3"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kho pana mayā adinnaṃ ādinnaṃ yāvatakaṃ vā tāvatakaṃ vā taṃ na suṭṭhu, "
"taṃ na sādhu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:8.4"
msgid ""
"Ahañceva kho pana tappaccayā vippaṭisārī assaṃ, na metaṃ pāpaṃ kammaṃ akataṃ "
"bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:8.5"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya tañceva adinnādānaṃ pajahati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:8.6"
msgid "Āyatiñca adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:8.7"
msgid "Evametassa pāpassa kammassa pahānaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:8.8"
msgid "Evametassa pāpassa kammassa samatikkamo hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:9.1"
msgid ""
"‘Bhagavā kho pana anekapariyāyena kāmesumicchācāraṃ garahati vigarahati, "
"kāmesumicchācārā viramathāti cāha."
msgstr "sexual misconduct …"

msgctxt "sn42.8:9.2"
msgid "Atthi kho pana mayā kāmesu micchā ciṇṇaṃ yāvatakaṃ vā tāvatakaṃ vā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:9.3"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kho pana mayā kāmesu micchā ciṇṇaṃ yāvatakaṃ vā tāvatakaṃ vā taṃ na "
"suṭṭhu, taṃ na sādhu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:9.4"
msgid ""
"Ahañceva kho pana tappaccayā vippaṭisārī assaṃ, na metaṃ pāpaṃ kammaṃ akataṃ "
"bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:9.5"
msgid ""
"So iti paṭisaṅkhāya tañceva kāmesumicchācāraṃ pajahati, āyatiñca "
"kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:9.6"
msgid "Evametassa pāpassa kammassa pahānaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn42.8:9.7"
msgid "Evametassa pāpassa kammassa samatikkamo hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:10.1"
msgid ""
"‘Bhagavā kho pana anekapariyāyena musāvādaṃ garahati vigarahati, musāvādā "
"viramathāti cāha."
msgstr "lying, saying: “Stop lying!”"

msgctxt "sn42.8:10.2"
msgid "Atthi kho pana mayā musā bhaṇitaṃ yāvatakaṃ vā tāvatakaṃ vā."
msgstr "But I have lied to a certain extent."

msgctxt "sn42.8:10.3"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kho pana mayā musā bhaṇitaṃ yāvatakaṃ vā tāvatakaṃ vā taṃ na suṭṭhu, taṃ "
"na sādhu. Ahañceva kho pana tappaccayā vippaṭisārī assaṃ, na metaṃ pāpaṃ "
"kammaṃ akataṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s not right, it’s not good, and I feel remorseful because of it. But I "
"can’t undo what I have done.’"

msgctxt "sn42.8:10.4"
msgid ""
"So iti paṭisaṅkhāya tañceva musāvādaṃ pajahati, āyatiñca musāvādā paṭivirato "
"hoti."
msgstr ""
"Reflecting like this, they give up lying, and in future they refrain from "
"lying."

msgctxt "sn42.8:10.5"
msgid ""
"Evametassa pāpassa kammassa pahānaṃ hoti. Evametassa pāpassa kammassa "
"samatikkamo hoti."
msgstr "That’s how to give up this bad deed and get past it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.322"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:11.1"
msgid "So pāṇātipātaṃ pahāya pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr "They give up killing living creatures."

msgctxt "sn42.8:11.2"
msgid "Adinnādānaṃ pahāya adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr "They give up stealing."

msgctxt "sn42.8:11.3"
msgid "Kāmesumicchācāraṃ pahāya kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr "They give up sexual misconduct."

msgctxt "sn42.8:11.4"
msgid "Musāvādaṃ pahāya musāvādā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr "They give up lying."

msgctxt "sn42.8:11.5"
msgid "Pisuṇaṃ vācaṃ pahāya pisuṇāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr "They give up divisive speech."

msgctxt "sn42.8:11.6"
msgid "Pharusaṃ vācaṃ pahāya pharusāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr "They give up harsh speech."

msgctxt "sn42.8:11.7"
msgid "Samphappalāpaṃ pahāya samphappalāpā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr "They give up talking nonsense."

msgctxt "sn42.8:11.8"
msgid "Abhijjhaṃ pahāya anabhijjhālu hoti."
msgstr "They give up covetousness."

msgctxt "sn42.8:11.9"
msgid "Byāpādappadosaṃ pahāya abyāpannacitto hoti."
msgstr "They give up ill will and malevolence."

msgctxt "sn42.8:11.10"
msgid "Micchādiṭṭhiṃ pahāya sammādiṭṭhiko hoti."
msgstr "They give up wrong view and have right view."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:12.1"
msgid ""
"Sa kho so, gāmaṇi, ariyasāvako evaṃ vigatābhijjho vigatabyāpādo asammūḷho "
"sampajāno paṭissato mettāsahagatena cetasā ekaṃ disaṃ pharitvā viharati, "
"tathā dutiyaṃ, tathā tatiyaṃ, tathā catutthaṃ. Iti uddhamadho tiriyaṃ "
"sabbadhi sabbattatāya sabbāvantaṃ lokaṃ mettāsahagatena cetasā vipulena "
"mahaggatena appamāṇena averena abyāpajjena pharitvā viharati."
msgstr ""
"That noble disciple is rid of desire, rid of ill will, unconfused, aware, "
"and mindful. They meditate spreading a heart full of love to one direction, "
"and to the second, and to the third, and to the fourth. In the same way "
"above, below, across, everywhere, all around, they spread a heart full of "
"love to the whole world—abundant, expansive, limitless, free of enmity and "
"ill will."

msgctxt "sn42.8:12.2"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, gāmaṇi, balavā saṅkhadhamo appakasireneva catuddisā viññāpeyya;"
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a powerful horn blower. They’d easily make themselves "
"heard in the four directions."

msgctxt "sn42.8:12.3"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, gāmaṇi, evaṃ bhāvitāya mettāya cetovimuttiyā evaṃ bahulīkatāya "
"yaṃ pamāṇakataṃ kammaṃ, na taṃ tatrāvasissati, na taṃ tatrāvatiṭṭhati."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when the heart’s release by love has been developed and "
"cultivated like this, any limited deeds they’ve done don’t remain or persist "
"there."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:13.1"
msgid ""
"Sa kho so, gāmaṇi, ariyasāvako evaṃ vigatābhijjho vigatabyāpādo asammūḷho "
"sampajāno paṭissato karuṇāsahagatena cetasā … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Then that noble disciple is rid of desire, rid of ill will, unconfused, "
"aware, and mindful. They meditate spreading a heart full of compassion …"

msgctxt "sn42.8:13.2"
msgid "muditāsahagatena cetasā … pe …."
msgstr "They meditate spreading a heart full of rejoicing …"

msgctxt "sn42.8:13.3"
msgid ""
"Upekkhāsahagatena cetasā ekaṃ disaṃ pharitvā viharati, tathā dutiyaṃ, tathā "
"tatiyaṃ, tathā catutthaṃ. Iti uddhamadho tiriyaṃ sabbadhi sabbattatāya "
"sabbāvantaṃ lokaṃ upekkhāsahagatena cetasā vipulena mahaggatena appamāṇena "
"averena abyāpajjena pharitvā viharati."
msgstr ""
"They meditate spreading a heart full of equanimity to one direction, and to "
"the second, and to the third, and to the fourth. In the same way above, "
"below, across, everywhere, all around, they spread a heart full of "
"equanimity to the whole world—abundant, expansive, limitless, free of enmity "
"and ill will."

msgctxt "sn42.8:13.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, gāmaṇi, balavā saṅkhadhamo appakasireneva catuddisā viññāpeyya;"
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a powerful horn blower. They’d easily make themselves "
"heard in the four directions."

msgctxt "sn42.8:13.5"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, gāmaṇi, evaṃ bhāvitāya upekkhāya cetovimuttiyā evaṃ "
"bahulīkatāya yaṃ pamāṇakataṃ kammaṃ na taṃ tatrāvasissati, na taṃ "
"tatrāvatiṭṭhatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when the heart’s release by equanimity has been developed "
"and cultivated like this, any limited deeds they’ve done don’t remain or "
"persist there.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn42.8:14.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, asibandhakaputto gāmaṇi bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, Asibandhaka’s son the chief said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn42.8:14.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bhante, abhikkantaṃ, bhante … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, sir! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "sn42.8:14.3"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may the Buddha remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn42.8:14.4"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
